# Gui install
install virtual box (https://www.virtualbox.org/)
install vagrant (http://www.vagrantup.com/)
install git for windows (http://msysgit.github.io/) with Git Bash
install rubyinstaller 1.9.3 (http://rubyinstaller.org/downloads/)
install rubyinstaller dev-kit (https://github.com/downloads/oneclick/rubyinstaller/DevKit-tdm-32-4.5.2-20111229-1559-sfx.exe) see https://github.com/oneclick/rubyinstaller/wiki/Development-Kit for details

# Windows PATH variable
Ensure that the VBoxManage.exe binary is on the path (C:\Program Files\Oracle\VirtualBox)

# windows command line:
gem install bundler

# Open Git Bash and within it type:
cd c:
mkdir Kitchen
cd Kitchen
mkdir sandbox
cd sandbox
git clone https://github.com/VlChef/sandbox.git .
bundle install
bundle exec kitchen create
bundle exec kitchen login
